    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<strong>欢迎参加布莽邦大乱斗！在这场整个星陨宇宙齐齐上阵的盛大赛事中，烂醉如泥的狂战熊、浑身辐射的鼻涕狼等各路豪杰将一较高下，争夺盖世巫妖的传奇面具。赢得大批粉丝支持，让主办人布莽邦的腰包鼓起来，助他重建一度辉煌的竞技场吧。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/f773c7a6b24bc4c744e0157c393ed7c8.poster.avif?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/f773c7a6b24bc4c744e0157c393ed7c8.webm?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/f773c7a6b24bc4c744e0157c393ed7c8.mp4?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/3ec8c707a20c5fe38cf8a19b363b9f7a.webp?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>打出卡牌，操纵盟友，在快节奏的战斗中战个你死我活。<br><br>想要赢下布莽邦大乱斗，关键不在公平竞争——而在赢得痛快。观众要的是精彩表演！用好变数牌，扭转乱斗的规则，为自己争取优势。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在单张卡牌上混搭多种升级，打造超强组合<br></li><li> 完成富有挑战性的壮举，让观众刮目相看，一步步提升战斗力<br></li><li> 从各持独特卡牌的8名英雄之中挑选3名，打造你的梦之队<br></li><li> 逾200张卡牌等你来发现，定能助你扭转战局</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/8491aad2aaf16bedb94368515f0b9a70.poster.avif?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/8491aad2aaf16bedb94368515f0b9a70.webm?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/8491aad2aaf16bedb94368515f0b9a70.mp4?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/2f7ce4f4280bfe8e82fc8f8873ea4fe2.webp?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>可怜的布莽邦正哭丧着脸。一天晚上，在星陨宇宙最边远的肮脏小酒馆里，他竟一时脑子犯傻，把自家竞技场的拥有权给赌没了。<br><br>第二天一早，他正闷闷不乐地在荒野上游荡，却碰见一副面具，其曾经的主人正是十恶不赦的盖世巫妖。他那棕灰脑袋里的齿轮便转了起来（虽然转得有点慢）。过了一会儿，绝无仅有的灵光闪过他的脑海：他可以把盖世巫妖的面具呈出来，充当新赛事的终极大奖，吸引技术最顶尖的英雄和出手最阔绰的观客，重建他那不可一世的竞技场！ <br><br>于是乎，这场宿命般的赛事初具雏形，随后还被冠以“布莽邦大乱斗”之名。然而布莽邦后来才意识到——当你跌落谷底时，生活有时候只会往你手上塞一把铲子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/28e5d5f77b72ce178a4155318dda44fb.webp?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>在竞技场上征战期间，你可以在旁边的布莽邦镇休整，找机会升级卡牌、训练英雄，又或者单纯欣赏风景。不过休息时间有限，可不够把想干的事全都做一遍，所以务必打好算盘，找准要光顾的小贩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/560228ecb981400d2e44375222a4a62b.poster.avif?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/560228ecb981400d2e44375222a4a62b.webm?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/560228ecb981400d2e44375222a4a62b.mp4?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/581d8f6b6e8b392d99dbc15e4b066079.webp?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>牌组构筑游戏的流程有时候耗时太久，不太尊重玩家的宝贵时间。《布莽邦大乱斗》从设计之初，就不止奔着深度和挑战性去，还兼顾了快餐式的玩法，供你随时随地快速来一局。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 单局流程平均时长不超过45分钟<br></li><li> 可解锁内容能拓宽战术选项，而又不至于强得破坏游戏平衡性<br></li><li> 游戏设置中就有选项可解锁完整内容</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/0a8748a468a0b8f7678e188f1ee9b4b2.poster.avif?t=1747368705\" width=542 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/0a8748a468a0b8f7678e188f1ee9b4b2.webm?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/0a8748a468a0b8f7678e188f1ee9b4b2.mp4?t=1747368705\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/bcc2a73adca326a469292459d5d4a909.webp?t=1747368705\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br>《布莽邦大乱斗》是《星陨传说》系列第三作。2017年系列首作《星陨传说》面世后，又在2019年马不停蹄推出了《星陨传说：流浪者的故事》。不过，想尽享《布莽邦大乱斗》的乐趣，也不是非得体验系列其他作品不可。每一作都有着非常不同的玩法机制，只是故事都发生在同一个宇宙，而且共享许多相同的角色。  <br><br>虽然有玩法上的差异，但是《布莽邦大乱斗》仍延续了系列传统——都以卡牌战斗为主题，都有滑稽的怪奇角色，还都不乏 roguelike 循环。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/ff65649596181de4656442263f9041b2.webp?t=1747368705\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2372950/extras/ff65649596181de4656442263f9041b2.poster.avif?t=1747368705\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=150 /></picture></span>",
